   Title: Hurricanes and Tropical Storms.
   Creator: Corporate Name: Southern Regional Climate Center (U.S.)
   Identifier: http://www.srcc.lsu.edu/OEP/tropical.html
   Subject: Hurricanes. Louisiana. Information resources.
   Subject: Hurricanes. Gulf Coast (U.S.). Information resources.
   Subject: Hurricanes. Mexico, Gulf of. Information resources.
   LC Classification: QC944
   Description: Includes current weather observations from the Southern
   Regional Climate Center, the latest satellite imagery from the
   Louisiana State University Earth Scan Laboratory, links to
   hurricane/tropical storm advisories and updates from the National
   Weather Service, and to other related information. Partial contents:
   Louisiana hourly observations (text) -- Coastal hourly wind
   observations (gif/text) -- Regional weather map -- NEXRAD imagery --
   Gulf of Mexico buoy observations -- Latest satellite imagery (visible,
   infrared, water vapor, color infrared).
